  (str title) (str `Page 2`)
  (str content) (str `2
LIST OF AMENDING ACTS
1. The Special Court (Trial of Offences Relating to Transactions in S e curi ties) A mendment Act,
1994 ( 24 of 1994 ).
2. The Special Court (Trial of Offences Relating to Transactions in Securities) Amendment Act,
1997 ( 6 of 1997 ).
_______
LIST OF ABBREVIATIONS USED
Cl., cls...... for Clause, clause s.
Ins......,, Inserted.
Notifn......,, Notification.
S., ss......,, Section, section s.
Sch......,, Schedule.
Subs......,, Substituted.
w.e.f......,, with effect from.`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str sourcePage) (int 2)
obj_root_law_sections_3:
